        "text": "Hi all :blush:\nSpeaker submissions are open for the <https:\/\/www.appsilon.com\/validated-ai-for-pharma-summit|Validated AI for Pharma Summit>, and we'd love to see some of you up there. It's a free virtual event on September 24, built for people working on AI, open source, and regulated pharma workflows.\nIf you're building, validating, or deploying AI in pharma, we want to hear how you're actually doing it. Topics we're especially keen on:\n• clinical trials and data-driven drug development\n• AI validation and regulatory compliance\n• open source tooling in pharma\n• taking AI from experimentation to production\nGot something to share? :raised_hands:<https:\/\/docs.google.com\/forms\/d\/e\/1FAIpQLSd5o4l2mOaZcdl0dBAGdXAZYxqMYHbYoZ18ghuzOzfYNgBG2Q\/viewform| Submit a talk here>!",
